-- Iran Ex-Minister to Run in 2013 Presidential Race, Donya Says
-- B y   Y e g a n e h   S a l e h i
-- 2012-08-09T09:31:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-09/iran-ex-minister-to-run-in-2013-presidential-race-donya-says.html
Former Iranian Commerce Minister
Mohammad Shariatmadari will run for president,  Donya-e-Eqtesad 
reported.  Shariatmadari, who served under former president Mohammad Khatami, will be a candidate in the 2013 race, the Tehran-based
newspaper reported, citing the political group, the Society for
Defending the Values of the  Islamic Revolution .  To contact the reporter on this story:
